item.title: re-frame trace
item.description: DevTools for re-frame This summer, we worked on a project that was focused on improving the developer experience with re-frame. We want to give an overview of the tool and summarize our contributions in the following post. The Joy of Debugging How often do you print something to the console? I do it quite often. My application does not work as expected and I need to go into various places in the code to figure out what is causing the problem.
